message: Harris turned around and filed, even more, charges against Backpage's execs, including repeating the pimping charge and adding in "Money laundering."

data.description: Late last year, we wrote about ridiculous charges by California's then Attorney General, Kamala Harris, against Backpage.com for "pimping." As we pointed out at the time, Harris clearly knew the case…
data.title: California Case Against Backpage Moves Forward Over Money Laundering Claims
